author: 千帆過盡
description:
When she woke up, she discovered that she slept with the male god.

But what does this long coveted meat taste like ……

Jian Xin said, “The first time, I didn’t get to taste it.”

Hua Chen said, “So, you want to try it again?”

Jian Xin: …if you don’t mind.

Hua Chen: You have such thick skin.

Jian Xin: I was a thin-skinned person, but when I thought of chasing you, how could my skin not turn thicker?>
